WEBVTT

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:31.816
Whether it is studies or life,

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:37.120
if it loses its liveliness,
then it becomes worthless.

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:45.936
And that is why our daughters
at the age of 12, left school

00:04:45.960 --> 00:04:48.136
and decided to turn to home-schooling.

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:52.860
Malvika and Radha did not even
take the board exam,

00:04:52.860 --> 00:04:56.080
which is usually considered
a must for a good career.

00:04:56.080 --> 00:05:02.160
The method we adopted for learning
is not a fool-proof studying method.